title: Suck It Tommy Trivia: The Back To School Edition + Plus This Nurse Did The Sweetest Thing For Her Patient
description:
So, normally when we play Suck It Tommy Trivia, Tommy asks us all trivia questions about movies (he’s not allowed to play because he knows basically EVERYTHING about Hollywood – he worked at Warner Brothers back in the day – and whoever gets it right gets to yell: “SUCK IT TOMMY!” Yeah. We know we’re 12. We don’t care. This round is all in honor of those going back to school.
